'''黑人的命也是命广场'''（{{lang-en|Black Lives Matter Plaza}}）（正式名称为'''西北区黑人的命也是命广场'''）是[[下城_(华盛顿哥伦比亚特区)|华盛顿特区市区]][[16街|16街]]其中的两个街道长的行人路段。<ref name="asmelash">{{Cite news|author=Asmelash|first=Leah|date=2020-06-06|title=Washington's New Black Lives Matter Street Mural Is Captured on Satellite|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/06/06/us/black-lives-matter-dc-street-mural-space-trnd/index.html|accessdate=2020-06-07|publisher=[[有线电视新闻网|CNN]]}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Johnson|first=Martin|date=2020-06-06|title=Bowser Addresses Record Crowd at Black Lives Matter Plaza|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/administration/501489-bowser-addresses-record-crowd-at-black-lives-matter-plaza|accessdate=2020-06-07|work=[[国会山报|The Hill]]|language=en}}</ref>该广场于2020年6月5日哥伦比亚特区公共工程部在地面上以{{Convert|35|ft|m|adj=Off}}的黄色大写字母绘词“[[Black_Lives_Matter|黑人的命也是命]]”，以及[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區旗|华盛顿特区]]的[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區旗|区旗]]，随后被哥伦比亚特区市长[[穆里尔·鲍泽|穆里尔·鲍泽]]改成现名，作为[[乔治·弗洛伊德之死引发的示威活动|乔治·弗洛伊德之死抗议活动]]的一部分。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Johnson|first=Ted|date=2020-06-06|title=DC Mayor Chides Donald Trump at Largest Protest Since Death of George Floyd: 'We Pushed the Army Away from Our City'|url=https://deadline.com/2020/06/d-c-black-lives-matter-mayor-donald-trump-1202952893/|accessdate=2020-06-07|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline]]|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607062908/https://deadline.com/2020/06/d-c-black-lives-matter-mayor-donald-trump-1202952893/|archivedate=2020-06-07}}</ref><ref name="aratani">{{Cite news|author=Aratani|first=Lauren|date=2020-06-06|title=Washington Mayor Stands Up to Trump and Unveils Black Lives Matter Mural|language=en-GB|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|location=London|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2020/jun/06/washington-mayor-muriel-bowser-trump|accessdate=2020-06-07|issn=0261-3077}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Google Maps, Bing Maps add marker for Black Lives Matter Plaza in Washington D.C.|url=https://www.digitaltrends.com/news/google-maps-black-lives-matter-plaza/|accessdate=2020-06-09|author=Mamiit|date=2020-06-09|first=Aaron|publisher={{tsl|en|Digital Trends||Digital Trends}}. digitaltrends.com}}</ref>

== 命名 ==
2020年6月5日，在[[乔治·弗洛伊德之死引发的示威活动|乔治·弗洛伊德抗议]]期间，哥伦比亚特区公共工程部在[[总统公园|总统公园]]的一部分[[白宫|白宫]]附近，[[拉法耶特广场_(华盛顿哥伦比亚特区)|拉法耶特广场]]北面的[[16街|16街]]上，在地面上以{{Convert|35|ft|m|adj=on}}的黄色大写字母绘词“[[Black_Lives_Matter|黑人的命也是命]]”，以及[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區旗|华盛顿特区]]的[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區旗|区旗]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dcist.com/story/20/06/05/ahead-of-saturday-protest-black-lives-matter-message-painted-on-16th-street-near-white-house/|title=DC Renames Intersection near White House 'Black Lives Matter Plaza' Paints 35-Foot Message on Street|date=2020-06-05|accessdate=2020-06-05|work=[[DCist|DCist]]|first=Mark|author=Austermuhle|first2=Daniella|author2=Cheslow|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605141623/https://dcist.com/story/20/06/05/ahead-of-saturday-protest-black-lives-matter-message-painted-on-16th-street-near-white-house/|archivedate=2020-06-05}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nbcwashington.com/news/local/dc-paints-black-lives-matter-on-street-near-lafayette-square/2323647/|title=City of DC Painting 'Black Lives Matter' on Street Near White House|date=2020-06-05|accessdate=2020-06-05|location=Washington, DC|publisher=[[WRC-TV|WRC-TV]]|first=Sophie|author=Barnes|first2=Justin|author2=Finch|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605141630/https://www.nbcwashington.com/news/local/dc-paints-black-lives-matter-on-street-near-lafayette-square/2323647/|archivedate=2020-06-05}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/06/05/us/black-lives-matter-dc-street-white-house-trnd/index.html|title=Washington DC Paints a Giant 'Black Lives Matter' Message on the Road to the White House|date=2020-06-05|accessdate=2020-06-05|publisher=CNN|first=AJ|author=Willingham|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605141621/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/06/05/us/black-lives-matter-dc-street-white-house-trnd/index.html|archivedate=2020-06-05}}</ref>同一天，哥伦比亚特区市长[[穆丽尔·鲍泽|穆里尔·鲍泽]]宣布，这条白宫附件的街道已正式更名为黑人的命也是命广场，并树立路牌。<ref>{{Cite news|first=Sophia|author=Barnes|first2=Justin|author2=Finch|title=City of DC Names Street to White House After Black Lives Matter; Emblazons Name on Road|url=https://www.nbcwashington.com/news/local/dc-paints-black-lives-matter-on-street-near-lafayette-square-street-renamed-black-lives-matter-way/2323647/|accessdate=2020-06-05|location=Washington, DC|publisher=WRC-TV|language=en-US|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605163403/https://www.nbcwashington.com/news/local/dc-paints-black-lives-matter-on-street-near-lafayette-square-street-renamed-black-lives-matter-way/2323647/|date=2020-06-05|archivedate=2020-06-05}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Wu|first=Nicholas|date=2020-06-05|title=DC Renames Street near White House 'Black Lives Matter Plaza' to Honor George Floyd Protests|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/06/05/black-lives-matter-mural-painted-near-white-house-mayors-behest/3153364001/|accessdate=2020-06-05|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|language=en-US|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605162259/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/06/05/black-lives-matter-mural-painted-near-white-house-mayors-behest/3153364001/|archivedate=2020-06-05}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|first=Susan|author=Heavey|first2=Steve|author2=Gorman|date=2020-06-07|title='A Part of History': Calm Prevails over DC's Biggest George Floyd Protest|language=en|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-minneapolis-protest-police-idUSKBN23C1A7|accessdate=2020-06-07}}</ref>宣布重命名时，她说：“[[布伦娜·泰勒之死|布雷娜·泰勒]]，在你生日那天，让我们坚定地站起来。”<ref>{{Cite news|title=DC Mayor Inaugurates 'Black Lives Matter' Plaza near White House|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/06/dc-mayor-inaugurates-black-lives-matter-plaza-white-house-200605193621540.html|accessdate=2020-06-07|work=Al Jazeera|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200606174528/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/06/dc-mayor-inaugurates-black-lives-matter-plaza-white-house-200605193621540.html|archivedate=2020-06-06}}</ref>她在新闻发布会上解释说：“有些人渴望听到和看到自己的人性。我们有机会在我们城市的一条非常重要的街道上大声疾呼地传达了这一信息。”<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-06-06|title=Mayor inaugurates 'Black Lives Matter Plaza' in DC with giant yellow letters|url=https://www.france24.com/en/20200606-mayor-inaugurates-black-lives-matter-plaza-in-dc-with-giant-yellow-letters|accessdate=2020-06-07|publisher=[[France_24|France 24]]|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|language=en}}</ref> 2020年10月，特区市议会投票决定永久保留该名称。<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-10-19|title=D.C. Council votes to permanently keep name 'Black Lives Matter Plaza'|url=https://wjla.com/news/local/dc-council-vote-tuesday-permanently-keep-name-black-lives-matter-plaza|publisher=[[WJLA|WJLA]]}}</ref>

许多人都认为这条街的名称不仅是对抗议活动的反应，也是抗议活动的一部分。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Mimetic Power of D.C.'s Black Lives Matter Mural|url=https://www.newyorker.com/culture/dept-of-design/the-mimetic-power-of-dcs-black-lives-matter-mural|accessdate=2020-06-09|author=Chayka|date=2020-06-09|first=Kyle|work=The New Yorker|language=en}}</ref>

鲍泽市长的决定是根据《哥伦比亚特区法典》<ref name="Politico 1">{{Cite news|author=Oprysko|first=Caitlin|date=2020-06-05|title=D.C. Government Dubs Intersection Where Police Cleared Peaceful Protesters 'Black Lives Matter Plaza'|work=[[Politico|Politico]]|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/06/05/black-lives-matter-plaza-washington-dc-303606|accessdate=2020-06-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607153927/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/06/05/black-lives-matter-plaza-washington-dc-303606|archivedate=2020-06-07}}</ref>的纪念性重命名城市街道的先例，重新命名了西北区16街该部分为公共聚会场所或广场。<ref name="DC Code 1">{{Cite web|title=Chapter 2. Street and Alley Closing and Acquisition Procedures|url=https://code.dccouncil.us/dc/council/code/titles/9/chapters/2/|accessdate=2020-06-07|year=2020|work=Code of the District of Columbia|publisher=DC Law Library|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607152243/https://code.dccouncil.us/dc/council/code/titles/9/chapters/2/|archivedate=2020-06-07}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title='Black Lives Matter Plaza,' Across From White House, Is Christened By D.C. Leaders|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/live-updates-protests-for-racial-justice/2020/06/05/870833518/black-lives-matter-plaza-across-from-white-house-is-christened-by-d-c-leaders|accessdate=2020-06-11|author=Dwyer|date=2020-06-05|first=Colin|work=NPR.org|language=en}}</ref>

== 地点 ==
[[File:Black_Lives_Matter_Plaza_Sign.jpg|替代=]]
该广场是西北区[[16街|16街]]的两个街区长的路段，向北与[[K街|K街]]交叉，中间穿过I街，并向南与[[H街|H街]]交叉；广场位于[[西北区_(华盛顿特区)|西北区]][[下城_(华盛顿哥伦比亚特区)|下城]]南部的[[总统公园|总统公园]]的北侧。<ref>{{Cite news|agency=Cox Media Group National Content Desk|title=Google Maps adds 'Black Lives Matter Plaza' after giant mural completed in Washington|url=https://www.kiro7.com/news/trending/google-maps-adds-black-lives-matter-plaza-after-giant-mural-completed-washington/CFJGMF2MBRDKJGRZNHZVBRWAV4/|date=2020-06-06|accessdate=2020-06-07|location=Seattle|publisher=[[KIRO-TV|KIRO-TV]]|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name="OSM">{{Cite web|title=Black Lives Matter Plaza|url=https://www.openstreetmap.org/?mlat=38.90099&mlon=-77.03649#map=19/38.90099/-77.03649|work=OpenStreetMap}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|first=Emily|author=Belfiore|date=2020-06-05|title=DC Mayor Changes Street Name to Black Lives Matter Plaza|url=https://www.eonline.com/news/1158968/washington-d-c-mayor-muriel-bowser-changes-street-name-to-black-lives-matter-plaza|accessdate=2020-06-07|work=E! Online}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple Maps updated with giant Black Lives Matter DC mural|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/6/8/21283744/black-lives-matter-satelliite-apple-maps|accessdate=2020-06-08|author=Ricker|date=2020-06-08|first=Thomas|work=The Verge|language=en}}</ref>尽管紧急车辆可以在左侧进入，但车辆的进入受到街道右侧的路障的阻挡。交通在K街和I街上不受影响。

